	Articles on Vegetarian Food:
Sri Chinmoy&#039;s students follow a vegetarian diet as part of their spiritual discipline, and many of the enterprises are cafes or restaurants that serve vegetarian food. Here are some related links on our sites

	
		Food for the Inner Quest - from the Irish Sri Chinmoy Centre site.
	
		Conscious Living by Jogyata Dallas from New Zealand
		 



	Restaurant &amp; Cafe Links:
All of these enterprises are owned and operated by students of Sri Chinmoy, serving tasty food and a peaceful atmosphere to the community around them.

	
		Ananda Fuara - San Francisco, California.
	
		Annam Brahma - Queens, New York.
	
		Annapurna - Toronto, Canada.
	
		Jyoti-Bihanga - San Diego, California.
	
		Perfection-Satisfaction-Promise - Ottawa.
	
		Silence-Heart-Nest - Seattle, Washington.
	
		The Blue Bird - Cafe in Auckland, New Zealand.
	
		The Lotus-Heart - Cafe-Restaurant in Christchurch, New Zealand.
	
		Victory&#039;s Banner - Chicago, Illinois.



