 <title>Christchurch Sri Chinmoy Centre</title>
 <link>http://www.srichinmoycentre.org/node/2339</link>
 <description>
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Christchurch, New Zealand&quot; class=&quot;right&quot; src=&quot;http://aum.vasudevaserver.netdna-cdn.com/cdn/farfuture/iKtR1ysOsSO0AVZ7gJIh-xRTwDqqkVno07BAIDHuJ-Q/mtime:1340034628/files/nz/sri_chinmoy_centres/scc_images/christchurch-city.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Christchurch, New Zealand&quot; /&gt;Established 2 June 1996&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;
	Photo Gallery&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://gallery.srichinmoycentre.org/nz/christchurch&quot;&gt;Christchurch Centre Photo Gallery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;
	Enterprises&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Following the 22 February 2011 earthquake which devastated Christchurch city, &lt;a href=&quot;http://thelotusheart.co.nz/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;The Lotus-Heart&lt;/a&gt; restaurant and health food store; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.gandharvaloka.co.nz&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Gandharva Loka&lt;/a&gt; world music store; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://thegiftshop.co.nz&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;The Gift Shop&lt;/a&gt; have all consolidated as a co-operative venture at 363 St Asaph Street (between Fitzgerald Avenue and Barbadoes Street). &amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://gallery.srichinmoycentre.org/nz/christchurch/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Photo Gallery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;
	Activities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Sri Chinmoy Centre regularly organises events and activities to help establish a balanced lifestyle of meditation, physical exercise and healthy living, integrating all parts of the being&amp;mdash;body, vital, mind, heart and soul&amp;mdash;to help bring forward our highest potentials and create a focused, dynamic, inspired and peaceful life. We warmly welcome you to any of the activities on our current programme of events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;
	Meditation Workshops&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For up-to-date information about meditation in Christchurch kindly visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://meditationchristchurch.org&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;MeditationChristchurch.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Sri Chinmoy Centre runs series of beginners meditation courses throughout the year. An excellent opportunity to learn the abc&amp;rsquo;s of meditation, have the uplifting experience of group meditation and to set up or gain inspiration for your personal meditation practise. Every course is different with different questions and different issues being addressed so there is always something new to learn. For information on our free meditation workshops kindly phone 377 1327, drop into The Lotus-Heart at 363 St Asaph Street, or use our &lt;a href=&quot;http://nz.srichinmoycentre.org/contact_nz&quot; title=&quot;Contact Us&quot;&gt;Contact Form&lt;/a&gt; to request information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Meditation Class Flyer 2005&quot; class=&quot;right&quot; src=&quot;http://aum.vasudevaserver.netdna-cdn.com/cdn/farfuture/l97DaGXX4TCA7MdrNviO5VQMt4fgsERIWx1oyNq-0ys/mtime:1325228943/files/nz/sri_chinmoy_centres/christchurch/class_flyer_2005&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Introduction to Meditation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	Meditation is natural and simple. Anyone can meditate. You simply need a yearning or curiosity to find out more about yourself, to lead a more peaceful and fulfilling life, and to be truly happy and healthy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Entry is free but registration is required. For more information kindly phone 377-1327.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.meditationchristchurch.org&quot;&gt;MeditationChristchurch.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn to &lt;a href=&quot;http://nz.srichinmoycentre.org/meditation&quot;&gt;meditate&lt;/a&gt; online resources.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;
	Concerts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity to relax, meditate and immerse yourself in the uplifting compositions of &lt;a href=&quot;http://nz.srichinmoycentre.org/sri_chinmoy&quot; title=&quot;Biography of Sri Chinmoy&quot;&gt;Sri Chinmoy&lt;/a&gt;. Using a variety of instruments from around the world, this sublime music is a unique blend of Eastern and Western traditions... a must for all lovers of vocal music. Followed by light refreshments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://nz.srichinmoycentre.org/sri_chinmoy_centres/christchurch/concerts&quot;&gt;More details...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Listen to the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.srichinmoy.tv/97/tv-archive/43/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;music&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information kindly phone 377-1327&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Photo gallery, &lt;a href=&quot;http://gallery.srichinmoycentre.org/nz/christchurch/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;click here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
